  3ÔåÆ## Tech-Stack
  4ÔåÆ
  5ÔåÆ| Technologie          | Zweck                                                           |
  6ÔåÆ| -------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |
  7ÔåÆ| **SvelteKit 2**      | Meta-Framework, SSR, Routing, Remote Functions                  |
  8ÔåÆ| **Svelte 5**         | Reaktives UI-Framework (Runes: `$state`, `$derived`, `$effect`) |
  9ÔåÆ| **Tailwind CSS 4**   | Utility-first Styling via `@tailwindcss/vite`                   |
 10ÔåÆ| **Bits UI / ShadCN** | Komponentenbibliothek in `src/lib/components/ui/`               |
 11ÔåÆ| **Drizzle ORM**      | Typsicherer SQL-Query-Builder                                   |
 12ÔåÆ| **Turso (LibSQL)**   | Serverlose SQLite-Datenbank                                     |
 13ÔåÆ| **better-auth**      | Authentifizierung (Google OAuth + E-Mail/Passwort)              |
 14ÔåÆ| **SuperForms + Zod** | Serverseitige Formularvalidierung                               |
 15ÔåÆ| **TanStack Table**   | Datentabellen (`@tanstack/svelte-table`)                        |
 16ÔåÆ| **i18next**          | Internationalisierung (10 Sprachen, Lazy Loading)               |
 17ÔåÆ| **docx**             | Word-Dokument-Generierung (.docx)                               |
 18ÔåÆ| **Lucide**           | Icons (`@lucide/svelte`)                                        |
 19ÔåÆ| **Bun**              | Paketmanager und Runtime                                        |
